This directory contains ClamAV databases and test files for the Bash antivirus project.

The contents of the directories are:
bash-antivirus
|- README                this file
|- databases
|  |- main.ndb           a complete database coming from ClamAV distribution
|  |- filtered.ndb       a filtered version for main.ndb, containing only signatures without metacharacters and without offset
|- eicar
|  |- *                  EICAR test files, infected by Eicar-Test-Signature (this signature is only in main.ndb)
|- test-files
|  |- *                  test files, where each file is infected by the virus that has the same name as the file
